(28, 'Toronto Junior Gloves', 'The Roeckl Toronto Junior Riding Gloves are super comfy, super stretchy gloves that have been specifically designed with teenage riders in mind, with a funky, glittering star design. \r\n\r\nThe exclusive comfort cut of the gloves ensures wearer comfort and fit and the fabric used on the palm is extremely wear-resistant and flexible, allowing an excellent contact on the reins. The back of the hand is made from 2-way Spandex and Lycra, there\'s a touch tape fastening on the wrist for an individual fit and a contrasting coloured trim and glitter star design. ', '1556338509_63020903_l.jpg', 2000, '{\"productName\":\"Toronto Junior Gloves\",\"price\":\"2000\",\"productCategory\":\"others\",\"description\":\"The Roeckl Toronto Junior Riding Gloves are super comfy, super stretchy gloves that have been specifically designed with teenage riders in mind, with a funky, glittering star design. \\r\\n\\r\\nThe exclusive comfort cut of the gloves ensures wearer comfort and fit and the fabric used on the palm is extremely wear-resistant and flexible, allowing an excellent contact on the reins. The back of the hand is made from 2-way Spandex and Lycra, there\'s a touch tape fastening on the wrist for an individual fit and a contrasting coloured trim and glitter star design. \",\"photo\":\"1556338509_63020903_l.jpg\",\"uploadDate\":1556338509}', '1556338509', 'Sports', 3, ''),
